cs.IT, cs.NI, cs.SY, cs.MM, cs.COM 

This paper deals with the outage performance of OFDM systems with decode-and-forward relays, which involves topics related to information theory (cs.IT), networking and internet architecture (cs.NI), systems and control (cs.SY), multimedia (cs.MM), and computer communication (cs.COM). The paper also discusses the optimization of system throughput, which is a common theme in many of these sub-categories.
